---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Interests" description="Exploring art, AI, finance, and their intersections">
  <Section id="interests-hero" className="pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Interests</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Exploring the intersection of art, artificial intelligence, and finance
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="art">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 p-8 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400">Art</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Creative expression through film, photography, and visual storytelling. Exploring how art can communicate 
          complex ideas and emotions, creating connections between people and experiences.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          From festival documentation to personal creative projects, art serves as a medium for exploration, 
          connection, and understanding the world around us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="ai">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 p-8 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400">Artificial Intelligence</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Discovering the intersection of artificial intelligence and creative processes. Exploring how AI can 
          enhance artistic expression and open new possibilities for creative work.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Learning about AI in collaborative settings, understanding complex concepts through shared exploration 
          and team-based learning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="finance">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 p-8 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400">Finance</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Understanding financial systems and their connection to creative endeavors. Exploring how financial 
          literacy can support creative projects and personal growth.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Learning about finance in practical, accessible ways, understanding how it intersects with art, 
          technology, and personal development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="intersection">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-accent-100 dark:from-primary-900/30 dark:to-accent-900/30 p-8 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-300">The Intersection</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          The most interesting work happens where these fields meet. Art informs technology, finance enables 
          creativity, and AI opens new artistic possibilities. Exploring these intersections creates opportunities 
          for innovation, understanding, and meaningful connection.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>

